About this site
Hello world! My name is Essie Zhang, and I am currently a UBC MDS student. I graduated from Boston University 2 years ago. This is my first time living in Canada. I am a huge dog person. My dog name is Yelo and she is a three years old shiba inu. I love jogging outside when the weather is nice.
